{"tid":1788620,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下18日波羅的海咁樣分配有冇問題","createTime":"2019-12-18T22:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T19:44:43.000Z","uid":69909,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff6b6a57fbccd1cd89155ebbdf336d9396e241a","tid":1788620,"uid":69909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T22:36:32.000Z","msg":"Vilnius入 Helsinki走<br />\n諗住Vilnius 3晚, Klaipeda 3晚因爲想去Curonian Spit<br />\n不過如果天氣唔好又去唔到 唔知5月多唔多雨<br />\nRiga 4晚, Tallinn 4晚, Helsinki 3晚<br />\nDay 7唔知會唔會太趕 但係唔想係Siauliai過夜<br />\n見到Klaipeda兩個鐘火車去到Siauliai 8:30am到Siauliai都應該ok<br />\n因爲十字架山應該都係逗留兩個鐘<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 10pm到Vilnius <br />\nDay 2 Vilnius <br />\nDay 3 Trakai<br />\nDay 4 朝早Vilnius去Kaunas行下 傍晚Kaunas去Klaipeda<br />\nDay 5 Klaipeda<br />\nDay 6 Nida/Curonian Spit<br />\nDay 7 朝早Klaipeda火車去Siauliai 去Hill of Crosses 跟住返Siauliai巴士去Riga<br />\nDay 8 Riga<br />\nDay 9 Rundāle Palace<br />\nDay 10 Sigulda<br />\nDay 11 朝早Riga上Tallinn<br />\nDay 12 Tartu<br />\nDay 13 Parnu<br />\nDay 14 Tallinn<br />\nDay 15 Tallinn to Helsinki<br />\nDay 16 Suomenlinna芬蘭堡<br />\nDay 17 Nuuksio National Park<br />\nDay 18 下晝機Helsinki走"},{"pid":"aa46cef1e17de611fe7067502b6d4c0fb877f9eb","tid":1788620,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T00:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6mqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=0451f390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax8